name: NBI Active U.S. Equity ETF
longDescription: The NBI Active U.S. Equity ETFs investment objective is to provide longterm capital growth. It invests, directly or indirectly through investments in securities of other mutual funds, in a portfolio comprised primarily of common shares of U.S. companies.
